title: late existencial crisis
body:
so I’ve been a fan of One Direction since like 7 years, but in a hardcore way.

when I was a child had everything of One Direction but I mean E V E R Y T H I N G, I watched the whole transmission they made of 7 hours for the 1Day, cried when they came to my continent but no to my country, watched all the tours/movie, bought their perfume, know every single one of their songs, cried for like 3 days when Zayn left and cried for like a week when they separate (they caused me a big depression inside of me, they leave me broke inside and it isn’t until now that I see that) but then I got over it until now.

so these few days I’ve listening all their songs and crying everytime I heard them bc it’s like I love them so fucking much and they were my happiness. I had a big happiness for like a year and a half just after they separate but then he left me and I move of country (AGAIN) bc of him and I just need they come back pls they make me so fucking happy and that’s it. I’m having a late late existencial crisis.
